Package: locClass
Version: 0.2-1
Date: 2010-06-07
Title: Collection of Local Classification Methods
Author: Julia Schiffner and Stefanie Hillebrand
Maintainer: Julia Schiffner <schiffner@statistik.tu-dortmund.de>
Depends: R (>= 2.10.0), methods, flexmix, party
Imports: stats, nnet, e1071, mvtnorm, sandwich
Suggests: mlbench, klaR, MASS, Matrix, SparseM, locClassData
Description: Collection of diverse local classification methods such as local versions of linear discriminant analysis, Fisher discriminant analysis and logistic regression.
